## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **dupilumab Dupixent 2024 COPD (BOREAS+NOTUS)** = first FDA biologic COPD — T2-high eosinophilic ≥300. IL-4Rα blockade — atopic dermatitis/asthma/EoE/CRSwNP/PN 후 COPD 확장. paradigm shift — COPD biologic era 개시. quantum-VQE 의 IL-4Rα Fab interface 직접 fit.
2. **ensifentrine Ohtuvayre 2024** = first FDA PDE3+PDE4 dual inhaler — first new COPD class in 20+ 년 (post-roflumilast 2011). ENHANCE Phase 3 + nebulized + bronchodilator + anti-inflammatory dual mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 dual-PDE pocket leverage.
3. **Trelegy Ellipta 2017 (fluticasone+umeclidinium+vilanterol)** = first FDA single inhaler triple ICS+LABA+LAMA — COPD + asthma 양쪽. compliance 향상 + GOLD E 상위 기준. Breztri Aerosphere 2020 두 번째.
4. **tiotropium Spiriva 2004** = first LAMA — once daily — COPD foundation. M3 selective. UPLIFT trial 4년 randomized 28,000 환자. mortality 영향 없음 — exacerbation reduction 한정.
5. **roflumilast Daliresp 2011** = first oral PDE4 — chronic bronchitis exacerbation reduction. nausea + weight loss + neuropsychiatric 부작용 제한적. ensifentrine 2024 dual inhaler 가 next.
6. **fazirsiran (Arrowhead) Phase 3 AATD** = SERPINA1 Z-mutant siRNA — α1-antitrypsin deficiency liver disease + emphysema 양쪽. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-oligonucleotide 결합 modeling (cross-hepatology).
7. **itepekimab Phase 3 AERIFY COPD** = anti-IL-33 — Sanofi/Regeneron — former smoker COPD. dupilumab 후 next biologic class. T2-low + T2-high 양쪽 가능성.
8. **α1-AT augmentation Prolastin/Aralast/Zemaira/Glassia 1987+** = AATD IV plasma-derived weekly infusion — emphysema progression slow. fazirsiran siRNA 가 disruptive alternative.
9. **smoking cessation varenicline+bupropion+NRT** = COPD progression 가장 영향 큰 intervention — non-pharmacology + behavioral. (cross-substance_use). 만성 흡연 cessation rate 한정 paradigm.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, COPD specific 임상 의미 한정. dupilumab BOREAS+NOTUS 결과 + ensifentrine ENHANCE 결과 = 2024 paradigm shift independent.

